<p class="p">We define the winter-summer ratio of the country-wise aggregated wind power generation as the ratio of the average winter wind generation 〈
 <italic class="italic">R</italic>〉
 <sub class="sub">DJF</sub> and the average summer wind generation 〈
 <italic class="italic">R</italic>〉
 <sub class="sub">JJA</sub>: 
